    <comment type="function">
      <text evidence="5">Class-II terpene synthase that synthesizes 8-hydroxy-copalyl diphosphate. Involved in the biosynthesis of cis-abienol, a labdane diterpene that can be used as synthesis precursor of ambergris substitution fragance products.</text>
    </comment>
